''''' Arkiv för Matematik''''' is a [[peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[Open access (publishing)|open-access]] [[mathematics journal]] of the [[Institut Mittag-Leffler]] of the [[Royal Swedish Academy of Sciences]]. The journal was established in 1949 when ''[[Arkiv för matematik, astronomi och fysik]]'' was split into separate journals, and is currently published by [[Springer Science+Business Media|Springer]].
The journal is indexed by ''[[Mathematical Reviews]]'' and [[Zentralblatt MATH]]. Its 2009 [[Mathematical Citation Quotient|MCQ]] was 0.47, and its 2009 [[impact factor]] was 0.455.
